<div class="container">
    <h1 style="color: var(--text-color);">Daily Plan: Thursday, January 15, 2026 (Feature Development)</h1>
    
    <div class="last-updated" style="color: var(--text-muted-color); font-size: var(--font-size-small);">
        <strong>Context:</strong> Week 3 Day 4 | 
        <strong>Focus:</strong> Complete Current Features & Close Blockers | 
        <strong>Last Updated:</strong> 2026-01-15
    </div>

    <h2>Focus: Drive Current Master Plan Item to Completion</h2>
    
    <div style="background: #e3f2fd; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Today's Objectives</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Complete Current Feature:</strong> Whatever Master Plan item was started - finish it</li>
            <li><strong>Resolve Blockers:</strong> Any issues blocking progress should be escalated/fixed</li>
            <li><strong>Test Changes:</strong> Verify all committed code works as expected</li>
            <li><strong>Prepare for Friday:</strong> If completing current item, identify which is next</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h3>Priority Matrix (Start with highest):</h3>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>A.3: Credentials Audit</strong> (CRITICAL) - Finish if started, or begin now</li>
        <li><strong>B.3: Theme Handling</strong> (HIGH) - Next option if A.3 complete</li>
        <li><strong>B.1: Docker Secrets</strong> (HIGH) - Strategic work</li>
        <li><strong>B.2: Authentication Fixes</strong> (HIGH) - Strategic work</li>
    </ol>

    <div style="background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ff9800; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 20px 0;">
        <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">Key Actions</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Push current work toward completion</li>
            <li>Create PR/commit any finished features</li>
            <li>Document what was completed</li>
            <li>Identify tomorrow's start point</li>
